In Loving Memory of Our Sweet Fur Baby, Kahlua.

It is with heavy hearts that we share the sad news of our beloved fur baby, Kahlua's passing. Eleven weeks ago, our big buddy left this world, just as he lived - on his own terms. Our hearts have been shattered, lives have been forever changed, and we have been turned upside down by the absence of our praying puppy.

Although the heartache is still fresh, we are slowly reaching a point where we can cherish the wonderful 7 years we were blessed to spend with Kahlua. Kahlua was so loved at home and he will forever live on in our hearts. We thank him so much for the smiles he put on our faces and joy he brought into our lives each and every day. 

Kahlua’s legacy, especially as the “praying puppy,” will endure, and we appreciate all his fans and collaborators around the world. Your friendship through Instagram and other social media platforms have been instrumental to the fame Kahlua was privileged to experience throughout his life. For all of you, we are forever grateful! 

Grief is a heavy burden - one that never truly lessens, but we learn to carry it as a testament to the love we had for Kahlua. Swayze, his constant companion and loyal baby brother, has been overwhelmingly sad since his big brother’s departure. They were inseparable and Swayze has never known a world without Kahlua by his side. Words can not describe the sadness and anxiety Swayze has been feeling recently. It was breaking our hearts watching Swayze go through such heartache.

Although we were not ready to move on as parents, we needed to do what was best for our little buddy, Swayze. That said, a few weeks ago, we took a step toward healing all of our hearts by welcoming a new fur friend into Swayze's life. While no one could ever replace his big brother, Kahlua, we hope that this addition to our family will help ease the pain.

Allow us to introduce Swayze's new brother, who is not just any pup, but actually his biological nephew – Whiskey.🐾

As we navigate this journey of grief we find solace in knowing that Kahlua's memory lives on and we honor him by giving love to Whiskey - just as we did with our sweet big buddy, Kahlua. #KuddlyKahlua
